SECTION 1 — Python (Core + Framework + Real Project Skills)
1. Practical Coding Questions

"You’re given a list of dictionaries representing user data. Filter users with age > 25 and sort them by name. Write the code."
"Write a Python function to remove duplicates from a list while maintaining order."
"Given a log file (as text), extract all email IDs using regex."

2. Framework / API Questions (Django/FastAPI/Flask)

"Explain the folder structure of your last Python project."
"Show me how you created an API endpoint in your project. Explain the flow."
"How did you handle authentication? JWT? Session? OAuth? Explain live."
"How did you connect Python backend to your database?"
"In FastAPI or Flask, how do you handle input validation?"

3. Hands-on Deep-Dive Questions

"Show me the most complex function you wrote in your project. Explain why you wrote it that way."
"Tell me about a bug you solved recently. How did you debug it?"
"Open your GitHub project and explain the architecture."

SECTION 2 — SQL (MySQL/PostgreSQL) Practical Questions
1. Query Writing (On-the-spot)

"Given tables employees and departments, write a query to find the top 2 highest paid employees in each department."
"Write SQL to find duplicate emails in a users table."
"Write SQL to get the month-on-month sales growth percentage."

2. Real-World Problem Questions

"Tell me about a stored procedure you built. What business problem did it solve?"
"Show me how you optimize a slow SQL query."
"Explain indexing. In your own project, which columns did you index and why?"

SECTION 3 — Frontend (HTML, CSS, JS, React)
1. Hands-on Coding Questions

"Build a responsive button with hover effect using CSS."

"Write JavaScript code to fetch API data and display it."

"Create a simple form page with validation (email + password)."

2. React / Modern Frontend Questions

"Explain how you structured your React components in your last project."

"Show me your favorite reusable component and explain its logic."

"How did you handle form management—Formik? React Hook Form?"

"How did you integrate your frontend with the backend API?"

3. Project-Based Assessment

"Show me your deployed website. What part of it did you build?"
"Open your GitHub repo and explain your folder structure."
"Tell me the hardest frontend challenge you solved."

